CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 26, 1961, pg. A13 reads: "Leaving Church - Mr. and Mrs. William Henry Lewis smile for the photographer as they leave St. Richard Roman Catholic Church, following their recent wedding. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: William Henry Lewis and Sheldon Juanita DeLaney Lewis cutting three tiered wedding cake, bride looking at groom, in interior with exposed pipes
